{"tid":1831491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet 的威力！在兩大無線台音樂節目蟬聯三週冠軍","createTime":"2020-01-20T12:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T10:12:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5342bed842db936f1f2ae22632367041d7c40ff5","tid":1831491,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"這次完全沒上節目打歌的 Red Velvet 成績依然驚人，&ldquo;Psycho&rdquo; 的十冠王頭銜也已近在眼前了！<br />\n<br />\n今天（19 日）在 SBS 播出的《人氣歌謠》中，Red Velvet 憑著改版專輯主打歌 &ldquo;Psycho&rdquo; 擊敗 Noel 和 SF9，連續三週拿下冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，昨天她們也才剛在 MBC《Show! 音樂中心》擊敗 IU 和昌模，同樣成功達成蟬聯三週冠軍的好成績。<br />\n<br />\n如此一來，Red Velvet 自從本月 3 日在 KBS 2TV《Music Bank》拿下回歸後首冠，&rdquo;Psycho&rdquo; 至今已累積八座冠軍獎盃，是繼 2018 年的 &ldquo;Power Up&rdquo; 以來的最佳成績！"},{"pid":"61128ab481dce5a4cf3c12dfc8002ff8224e49dd","tid":1831491,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/5eb1efa835ed59760a3bf102ab6f2494/3e596b1768620a1b-cf/s400x600/9f39ff9bc14e7f5ecd3c452ffdabef1aa6a09a7c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F5eb1efa835ed59760a3bf102ab6f2494%2F3e596b1768620a1b-cf%2Fs400x600%2F9f39ff9bc14e7f5ecd3c452ffdabef1aa6a09a7c.gifv&h=a9b198ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/e9dbecb635a8d8facb4a70844746275f/7d17e9016048ad7c-ef/s540x810/be116030b4465446c6e50b77e83a24027bf675ff.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fe9dbecb635a8d8facb4a70844746275f%2F7d17e9016048ad7c-ef%2Fs540x810%2Fbe116030b4465446c6e50b77e83a24027bf675ff.gifv&h=f0b6789b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRV forever<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae77a979ec478b832a122b4ec4c0ffe1330d180","tid":1831491,"uid":228907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"的確係好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla